          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0379P0_20020130_WH_107' title='Link to this speech by Mr Nicholas Winterton' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-nicholas-winterton" title="Mr Nicholas Winterton">Mr. Deputy Speaker</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            Order. I am going to use my discretion and say that time is up&#x2014;
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0379P0_20020130_WH_108'>  </a>
